Package ohos.agp.database

Class DataSetPublisher

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.agp.database.Publisher<DataSetSubscriber>
      • ohos.agp.database.DataSetPublisher

  • public class DataSetPublisher
extends Publisher<DataSetSubscriber>
    Notifies a dataset subscriber of detected dataset changes.

    This class extends the Publisher class of the DataSetSubscriber type. It is used to notify the dataset subscriber when the dataset changes or the dataset is invalidated.

    Since:
    3
    See Also:
    DataSetSubscriber, Publisher

    • Method Detail

      • notifyChanged

        public void notifyChanged​()
        Notifies the subscriber that the subscribed data has changed.

        When the data changes, this method is used to call the DataSetSubscriber#onChanged interface of each subscriber for handling the changes.

      • informInvalidated

        public void informInvalidated​()
        Notifies the subscriber that the subscribed data becomes invalid.

        When the data becomes invalid, this method is used to call the DataSetSubscriber#onInvalidated interface of each subscriber to notify the subscriber.

        Since:
        4

      • notifyItemChanged

        public void notifyItemChanged​(int position)
        Notifies the subscriber that the subscribed item data has changed.

        When the item data changes, this method is used to call the DataSetSubscriber#onItemChanged(int) interface of each subscriber for handling the changes.

        Parameters:
        position - Indicates the position of the item in the data set.
